  "text": "Our method compares favorably to primitive-based cloud animation systems in several ways. Traditional key-framing and particle systems [CITATION_1] require tedious editing of the ellipsoid primitives constituting the clouds and do not scale for authoring large scenes. In contrast, our approach allows to manipulate large cloudscapes easily.",
